```{r setup, include=FALSE}
require(psych)
require(tidyverse)

head_tail <- function (df, n = 3, caption = "") {
  psych::headTail(df, top = n, bottom = n) %>% knitr::kable(caption = caption)
}
```

# Nav-bar

### [Navigation Bar ](https://rmarkdown.rstudio.com/flexdashboard/using.html#navigation_bar){target="_blank" title="flexdashboard for R"}

  

![](./fig/navbar.png)  
YAML`output`  
  

```
---
output: 
  flexdashboard::flex_dashboard:
    navbar:
      - { title: "Prev", icon: "fa-chevron-circle-left", href: ""}
      - { title: "Next", icon: "fa-chevron-circle-right ", href: ""}
    social: [ "menu" ]
    source_code: embed
---
```

  

   | 
-------|-----------------------------
navbar | HTML
social | SNS
source_code | flexdashboards
